  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #396743

*freetts-1.2.1-r2 (23 Mar 2011)

  23 Mar 2011; Christopher Brannon <cbrannon@gentoo.org>
  freetts-1.2.1-r1.ebuild, +freetts-1.2.1-r2.ebuild:
  Change the directory in which we look for mbrola.
  This requires a revbump. The new revision depends on
  app-accessibility/mbrola-3.01h-r6.
  app-accessibility/freetts-1.2.1-r1's dependencies 
were adjusted, since it will not work with
app-accessibility/mbrola-3.01h-r6.

  17 Jul 2008; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  add GLEP 56 USE flag desc from use.local.desc

  23 Oct 2007; William L. Thomson Jr. <wltjr@gentoo.org>
  -freetts-1.2.ebuild, -freetts-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Removed java gen 1 ebuilds

